DBLibraryDriver - Class in <Unnamed>
Before you compile in DrJava, go to Edit > Preferences > Resource Locations Press the Add button under Extra Path to add the following two jars: 1- /usr/people/classes/CS230/handouts/project/DatabaseLibrary/csci230databaselibrary.jar 2- /usr/people/classes/Java/mysql-connector-java-3.1.10-bin.jar To run, issue: java DBLibraryDriver "YourDatabaseUsername" "YourDatabasePassword" in the Interactions Pane in Dr.
